SMAFormulaDesc = SMA = Sum of last %s months demand / %s. Equal weight to all periods.
WMAFormulaTitle = Weighted Moving Average
WMAFormulaDesc = WMA = Sum(qty x weight) / Sum(weights). Recent months weighted more heavily (e.g. 3-month: weights 3,2,1).
SeasonalFormulaTitle = Seasonal Index
SeasonalFormulaDesc = Seasonal Index = Month Average / Overall Monthly Average. Index > 1 means above-average demand for that month.
MAPEFormulaDesc = MAPE = Mean Absolute Percentage Error = (1/n) x Sum(|actual - forecast| / actual) x 100. Lower is better.
