ROPFormulaTitle = Reorder Point (ROP)
ROPFormulaDesc = ROP = (Avg Daily Demand x Lead Time) + Safety Stock. Reorder when current stock falls to this level.
SSFormulaTitle = Safety Stock
SSFormulaDesc = Safety Stock = Z x Sigma(daily demand) x Sqrt(Lead Time). Z-score from service level: 90%%=1.28, 95%%=1.65, 99%%=2.33
EOQFormulaTitle = Economic Order Quantity
EOQFormulaDesc = EOQ = Sqrt(2 x D x S / H). D = annual demand, S = cost per order, H = annual holding cost per unit.
BOMExplosionFormulaTitle = BOM Explosion
BOMExplosionFormulaDesc = Cascades demand for a finished product through its Bill of Materials to calculate raw material requirements.
